  "title": "Field Service Technician",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>• Provide field service support for water treatment</p><p>• Provide testing and on-site water management services at customers plants</p><p>• Check chemical dosing and monitoring equipment and carry out repair when necessary</p><p>• Carry out disinfection of cooling towers</p><p>• Conduct site survey and obtain samples for laboratory analysis</p><p>• Maintain housekeeping at allocated areas within customer premises<br /></p><p>Job Requirement:</p><p>• Higher NITEC qualifications</p><p>• Minimum 1-2 years in providing on-site service works in the field of cooling/boiler water</p><p>treatment</p><p>• Good understanding of plant equipment and chemical treatment program applied</p><p>• Able to interact with customers and assist in enhancing customer satisfaction</p><p>• Assist account manager/engineer in start-up of chemical treatment program and</p><p>troubleshooting in customer facilities</p><p>• Computer literate and must have Class 3 Driving License</p><p>Working hours:</p><p>• Monday to Friday from 8.30am to 5pm</p>",
